@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}


<style>
    body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #E55D87, #5FC3E4);
        color: white;
        line-height: 1.6;
    }

    h1 {
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 4rem;
        margin-bottom: 30px;
        text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
    }

    p {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        text-align: justify;
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
    }

    strong {
        color: #FFC300;
    }
</style>

<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

<p>Welcome to our <strong>totally legit</strong> privacy policy page! Here at <strong>Random Movie Generator</strong>, we take your privacy <em>very</em> seriously. In fact, we're so serious about it, we wrote this policy just for you!</p>

<p>As you browse our website, you might notice we collect absolutely <strong>zero</strong> personal information. That's right, we don't even know who you are, and frankly, we like it that way. It's a win-win situation: you remain anonymous, and we have less data to worry about!</p>

<p>Now, we do have a cookie policy... but it only applies to the delicious chocolate chip cookies we eat while coding. We can assure you that <strong>no cookies</strong> are used for tracking you on our site. If you find one, it's probably a leftover crumb from our snack break.</p>

<p>Feel free to share your thoughts, opinions, and even your deepest secrets in our comments section. Just remember that we're not responsible for any top-secret information you accidentally leak. Always be cautious with your privacy, especially when discussing your <strong>world domination plans</strong>!</p>

<p>So, sit back, relax, and enjoy our site without worrying about your privacy. And if you have any questions, just remember: we have no idea who you are, so there's not much we can do to help you!</p>
